1
00:00:48,310 --> 00:00:52,990
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:56,000
[Episode 21]

3
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,210
Zhao Li!

4
00:01:06,870 --> 00:01:07,730
I've come back?

5
00:01:09,870 --> 00:01:11,039
With just a thought,

6
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,680
your mind is full of Zhao Li.

7
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:17,760
You even conjured up
some beat-up gun out of nowhere.

8
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,950
You killed Situ Fei,

9
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,789
and the cyber world he created

10
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:21,590
disappeared.

11
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:23,150
So naturally, you came back.

12
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:23,760
Thank you.

13
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,460
Even though you are a night watchman,

14
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,950
you still took a huge risk

15
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,400
to help us demons.

16
00:01:31,950 --> 00:01:33,280
I haven't told you this,

17
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:35,400
but my night watchman speech

18
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,330
has a different background music.

19
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:41,080
Our night watchmen,

20
00:01:41,509 --> 00:01:43,479
empowered by the righteousness
of heaven and earth,

21
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,310
are dedicated to eliminating evil

22
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:47,150
and demonic deeds in the world.

23
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,920
You little demon,

24
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:51,039
if you do bad things,

25
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,020
I can't stop you right now.

26
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:55,280
But if you do bad things when you grow up,

27
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:58,150
I will still hunt you down.

28
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,960
They won't do bad things.

29
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,740
We will let them know

30
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,170
that humans saved them.

31
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,360
They won't turn bad.

32
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:07,270
Right.

33
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,490
Those employee badges

34
00:02:08,490 --> 00:02:10,090
should have all fallen down.

35
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:10,750
Yeah.

36
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:12,910
They can take

37
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:14,110
their children home.

38
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,560
Let's go home too.

39
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:17,960
Okay.

40
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,270
Let's go home.

41
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,240
Actually,

42
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,600
I have a lot of

43
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:31,690
background music.

44
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,960
The oppression dissipates.

45
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,800
All beings flee.

46
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,680
The seeds of good and evil

47
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:40,190
will gain the soil of new life.

48
00:02:41,010 --> 00:02:41,970
Those who do good

49
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,030
will eventually
bathe in the light of heaven.

50
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:47,470
Evildoers can't escape
sinking into the abyss.

51
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:48,190
Fei,

52
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:49,950
what happened to you?

53
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,120
Poor thing.

54
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:56,630
Who hit you?

55
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,720
Xia Dongqing.

56
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,290
Do you know him?

57
00:02:59,590 --> 00:03:00,520
Xia Dongqing?

58
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,840
He has such skills?

59
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:03,840
He used the power

60
00:03:03,870 --> 00:03:05,190
of the former ghost messenger.

61
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:07,120
There was also a night watchman
next to him.

62
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:07,920
Zhao Hengzhi?

63
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:12,360
They killed you

64
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:13,520
in your world?

65
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:14,870
Yes.

66
00:03:15,590 --> 00:03:17,030
In the cyber world,

67
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:19,680
once a thought arises, it becomes reality.

68
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,910
You shouldn't have left

69
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,280
this loophole in the first place.

70
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,910
I don't have time to talk about this.

71
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,770
Save me, quick!

72
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:30,520
You've already been killed by him.

73
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,150
How can I save you?

74
00:03:33,250 --> 00:03:34,190
Put my remaining consciousness

75
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:35,300
into your world.

76
00:03:35,910 --> 00:03:36,710
Reprogram

77
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,030
and regenerate my body.

78
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,680
I don't know how to do that.

79
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,280
Then find someone who does!

80
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,250
Yan Yuzhen.

81
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:47,020
Do you remember our ideal?

82
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:48,400
Do you remember how you exist

83
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,280
in this world?

84
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:51,440
You women really...

85
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,800
don't know what matters.

86
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,960
Don't attack women.

87
00:03:57,150 --> 00:03:58,030
Right now,

88
00:03:58,190 --> 00:04:00,390
you still need a woman to save your life.

89
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,000
Don't underestimate women.

90
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,120
The woman in front of you

91
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,800
has already learned your tricks.

92
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,630
Of course, I haven't forgotten

93
00:04:11,630 --> 00:04:12,620
our ideal,

94
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:15,630
to merge demonic magic with technology

95
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:17,510
and create a new world

96
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,220
by connecting the old and new worlds.

97
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,560
We are

98
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,750
the Fuxi and Nuwa

99
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,970
of the new world.

100
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,720
Then save me quickly.

101
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,600
No.

102
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,980
I looked through the earliest myths,

103
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:38,310
and Fuxi

104
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,830
doesn't feature in them.

105
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,000
Perhaps,

106
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:45,560
this world

107
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:46,970
doesn't need

108
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,070
a Fuxi at all.

109
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,320
Yuzhen, save me!

110
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:03,720
Save me!

111
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:04,980
Save me, Yan Yuzhen!

112
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,100
Yan Yuzhen, you...

113
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,920
God Fei is so handsome!

114
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:20,340
[Ten years ago]

115
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,160
I like him so much.

116
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,120
My goodness,

117
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,830
I wonder

118
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:17,870
when I can see him.

119
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:19,360
God Fei is really effective!

120
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,510
I go to his homepage every day.

121
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,390
Yeah.

122
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,190
Hello.

123
00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:25,090
The god you mentioned

124
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,600
can divine the future

125
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:28,160
and grant your wishes,

126
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:28,630
right?

127
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,040
Can you tell me his address?

128
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:32,630
God Fei doesn't have a residence.

129
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,750
He's a virtual god.

130
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,310
A virtual god?

131
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,190
God Fei is an internet god.

132
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:39,120
But he's really effective.

133
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,830
No top-up needed.

134
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,920
Just light 3 electronic incense sticks

135
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,380
on his homepage every day.

136
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,460
It's just a tap of a finger.

137
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:49,770
So this is the god you were talking about.

138
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,190
Fei.

139
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:54,720
Fei.

140
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,010
Who is it?

141
00:05:58,840 --> 00:05:59,400
A demon?

142
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,420
How did you get in here?

143
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:03,360
This is the world of gods.

144
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,240
Fei,

145
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:07,040
the giant demon of the North Sea

146
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,570
recorded
in the "Classic of Mountains and Seas."

147
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:09,840
Weren't you slain

148
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,200
thousands of years ago?

149
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,720
A small group of humans resurrected me.

150
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,510
They discussed my life

151
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,600
on the internet,

152
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:17,750
drew my image,

153
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,830
and summoned my remnant soul

154
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:20,430
from the void,

155
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,350
so I became the me you see now,

156
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,600
God Fei made of code.

157
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,360
You live in such a small place.

158
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,380
Don't call yourself a god,

159
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,070
okay?

160
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,620
I am collecting faith.

161
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:37,290
It will increase my power.

162
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,240
Would you consider

163
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,950
combining demonic power with code?

164
00:06:44,450 --> 00:06:45,850
Demonic power with code?

165
00:06:46,310 --> 00:06:47,440
I think it will work.

166
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:49,159
Although

167
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:51,920
I don't know how to operate it,

168
00:06:52,650 --> 00:06:53,240
as long as

169
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,600
the two of us combine,

170
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,390
maybe...

171
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:57,920
perhaps...

172
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:01,360
it only takes 10 years

173
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,560
to create a great world.

174
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:06,390
Only those who dominate such a world

175
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,240
can be called gods.

176
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,520
You really are

177
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,000
talking to yourself

178
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,750
and being delusional.

179
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:13,680
Even if I conquer

180
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,850
technical problems,

181
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:16,000
to create a great world,

182
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,950
do you know how much
demonic power it takes?

183
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:18,560
Just you?

184
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,920
You don't have much demonic power either.

185
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:21,560
But

186
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,160
I'm intelligent.

187
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,030
Let's cooperate once

188
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,320
to see if it'll work.

189
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,950
I will make you

190
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,159
the God of Creation.

191
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,070
Farewell,

192
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,159
Fei.

193
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,190
At the beginning of creation,

194
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,430
when the world was first opened,

195
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,120
God said,

196
00:07:58,430 --> 00:07:59,630
"Let there be light."

197
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,240
What is it?

198
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,360
It's bulging.

199
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:25,800
What are you doing?

200
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,800
Give it back to me.

201
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:28,970
You still have it.

202
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,300
This thing in this space

203
00:08:30,300 --> 00:08:31,160
can't turn into a gun.

204
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,669
I like it, so I'll carry it.

205
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,380
Okay, you carry it.

206
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,610
This is the Ferry Man's gun?

207
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:39,429
Zhao Li's gun.

208
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,200
What were you thinking at that time

209
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,669
to suddenly conjure up this gun?

210
00:08:42,669 --> 00:08:43,600
I thought,

211
00:08:44,550 --> 00:08:45,680
if Zhao Li were here,

212
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,910
it would be great.

213
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:47,840
What do you mean?

214
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,720
I just felt you couldn't defeat him.

215
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,650
Where are you going?

216
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:54,810
To have breakfast.

217
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,720
I-It's not that you couldn't defeat him.

218
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,380
It was just a little struggle.

219
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,150
That outfit you wore inside

220
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,210
is quite handsome.

221
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,400
It's also Zhao Li's?

222
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,760
Were the clothes

223
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,250
you changed into ancient?

224
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,710
That's our ancestor's.

225
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,200
I am not capable?

226
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,380
I'm very powerful.

227
00:09:16,210 --> 00:09:16,900
Hello.

228
00:09:20,750 --> 00:09:21,270
What?

229
00:09:23,150 --> 00:09:24,270
I'll be right there!

230
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:25,200
Which hospital?

231
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,030
The patient's vital signs are normal,

232
00:09:27,030 --> 00:09:28,360
but she hasn't woken up.

233
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,000
We took a scan of her,

234
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,360
and it seems she is

235
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:32,530
in a deep sleep.

236
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,510
Sleep?

237
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:37,080
So what is her exact condition now?

238
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,960
And... our child?

239
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,150
The child is fine.

240
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,080
It's just...

241
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,480
Just what?

242
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,850
You'd better go inside and see.

243
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:00,480
Is this Ya?

244
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:08,210
Doctor, what happened to her?

245
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:09,560
I don't know why,

246
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:10,440
but the patient has fallen

247
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,970
into a state of rapid aging.

248
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,740
A state of rapid aging.

249
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:28,440
Ya.

250
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,380
What's wrong with you?

251
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,080
You... you... you...

252
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,750
How did you become like this?

253
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,210
You are a Heavenly Maiden.

254
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,330
A Heavenly Maiden.

255
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,360
It is the Five Declines.

256
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:48,220
When immortals' lifespan nears its end,

257
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:50,750
they exhibit Five Declines.

258
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,270
Ya.

259
00:12:10,550 --> 00:12:11,150
Where am I?

260
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,670
You are home.

261
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:18,440
Kunlun?

262
00:12:18,870 --> 00:12:20,330
How did I return to Kunlun?

263
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,950
Because you are about to give birth.

264
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:24,670
Whenever Heavenly Maidens give birth,

265
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,930
they return to Kunlun.

266
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,050
Go back and rest.

267
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:31,510
You will be in labor soon.

268
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,120
If not tomorrow,

269
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:34,610
it will be tonight.

270
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:46,150
[Chapter 11] [Kunlun]

271
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,230
If I stay in Kunlun,

272
00:12:46,230 --> 00:12:47,890
what will happen to Dongqing?

273
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,320
If Dongqing can't find me,

274
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,380
he will be worried.

275
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,870
This is our child.

276
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:53,750
When I give birth,

277
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:56,130
if Dongqing isn't by my side,

278
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,320
he will blame me.

279
00:12:57,630 --> 00:12:59,160
I must return to the human world.

280
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,480
I must be by Dongqing's side.

281
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,030
Ya,

282
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,030
relax.

283
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,630
Look.

284
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:12,030
Dongqing.

285
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,120
Ya.

286
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:23,470
Dongqing,

287
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,050
why are you here?

288
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,370
Of course, I am here.

289
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,630
I will always be by your side.

290
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:31,270
Especially,

291
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,030
I want to see

292
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:34,000
our child come

293
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:36,170
into this world with my own eyes

294
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:37,870
and hear

295
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,960
our child's

